Chemicals: {{ drug.name }} ({{ batch_number }}) and naproxen sodium ({{ batch_number }}) reference standards were obtained from {{ drug.pharmacopoeia_standard }} (Rockville, MD) and used for the {{ drug.strength }} and {{ drug.strength }} studies. All solvents were {{ drug.molecular_formula }} grade (Avantor Performance Materials, Inc., Phillipsburg, NJ) and all reagents were analytical grade (Mallinkrodt Baker, Inc., Phillpsburg, NJ).
